Toamasina.title: Toamasina
Toamasina.byline: Toamasina is a port city on the east coast of Madagascar.

Toa Alta.title: Toa Alta
Toa Alta.byline: Toa Alta is a municipality and town of 67,000 residents located in the Toa Valley region of San Juan's metropolitan area in Puerto Rico along the island's Atlantic coast.
